name: Apororhynchus
description: Apororhynchida<-- This template has to be warmed up before it can be used, for some reason -->Apororhynchida is an order containing one family, Apororhynchidae, [1] and one genus, Apororhynchus, [1] of microscopic parasitic worms that attach themselves to the intestinal wall of terrestrial vertebrates.
